1. Task Description
    https://adventofcode.com/2020/day/3

2. Summary:
    Given a pattern:
        start on top left open square
        move 3 right, 1 down
        move until below bottom-most row is passed
        count number of trees encountered

3. Example:
    . = Open square
    # = Tree

    Base pattern:
        ..##.......
        #...#...#..
        .#....#..#.
        ..#.#...#.#
        .#...##..#.
        ..#.##.....
        .#.#.#....#
        .#........#
        #.##...#...
        #...##....#
        .#..#...#.#

    Repeating many times:
        ..##.........##.........##.........##.........##.........##.......  --->
        #...#...#..#...#...#..#...#...#..#...#...#..#...#...#..#...#...#..
        .#....#..#..#....#..#..#....#..#..#....#..#..#....#..#..#....#..#.
        ..#.#...#.#..#.#...#.#..#.#...#.#..#.#...#.#..#.#...#.#..#.#...#.#
        .#...##..#..#...##..#..#...##..#..#...##..#..#...##..#..#...##..#.
        ..#.##.......#.##.......#.##.......#.##.......#.##.......#.##.....  --->
        .#.#.#....#.#.#.#....#.#.#.#....#.#.#.#....#.#.#.#....#.#.#.#....#
        .#........#.#........#.#........#.#........#.#........#.#........#
        #.##...#...#.##...#...#.##...#...#.##...#...#.##...#...#.##...#...
        #...##....##...##....##...##....##...##....##...##....##...##....#
        .#..#...#.#.#..#...#.#.#..#...#.#.#..#...#.#.#..#...#.#.#..#...#.#  --->

    Toboggan trail marked:
        O = open square
        X = Tree

        ..##.........##.........##.........##.........##.........##.......  --->
        #..O#...#..#...#...#..#...#...#..#...#...#..#...#...#..#...#...#..
        .#....X..#..#....#..#..#....#..#..#....#..#..#....#..#..#....#..#.
        ..#.#...#O#..#.#...#.#..#.#...#.#..#.#...#.#..#.#...#.#..#.#...#.#
        .#...##..#..X...##..#..#...##..#..#...##..#..#...##..#..#...##..#.
        ..#.##.......#.X#.......#.##.......#.##.......#.##.......#.##.....  --->
        .#.#.#....#.#.#.#.O..#.#.#.#....#.#.#.#....#.#.#.#....#.#.#.#....#
        .#........#.#........X.#........#.#........#.#........#.#........#
        #.##...#...#.##...#...#.X#...#...#.##...#...#.##...#...#.##...#...
        #...##....##...##....##...#X....##...##....##...##....##...##....#
        .#..#...#.#.#..#...#.#.#..#...X.#.#..#...#.#.#..#...#.#.#..#...#.#  --->

    Answer: 7 trees encountered.

4. Run the program
    cd AoC_2020_Day_3
    make run

5. Run the tests
    cd AoC_2020_Day_3
    make test

